</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C34976E3389B449CBBD233EA0B346D6B" pageId="4" pageNumber="159">Holotype, 1♂, Brunei/Temburong, Kuala Belalong FSC, 60-300 m, 16-20. IV. 1993, mixed Dipterc. for., E. Heiss, MHNG ENTO 00008955 (MHNG).</paragraph>
